extensions.description: Deep Value Investments (DVI) is developing a multi-asset digital marketplace built from the ground up for Cryptocurrency, NFTs, Equities, Fixed Income, Commodities, and FOREX. DVI is a first-to-market solution delivering a singular platform designed to encompass all cryptocurrency and investment needs for retail investors, institutional prime services (SaaS, TAMP, Operations, etc.), and RIA SaaS offerings.
